Actions a player can do:
	buy a property
	pay rent
	buy a house on a property
	buy a hotel on a property
	roll dice
	go to jail
	attempt to get out of jail
	pay to get out of jail
	recieve free parking money
	draw a card

What a player has to keep track of:
	Money
	owned properties
	in jail/out of jail
	number of utilities owned
	number of railroads owned
	which monopolies it owns
